<title>lḥbk ạ̉sẖtạq</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 lḥbk ạ̉sẖtạq ạ̉yạ syd lsẖkẖṣk ạ̉ḥtạj fkn mrsẖdy
 tsẖtạq nfsy llrb ạ̉n trạk tryd ạ̉n tʿwd lḥmạk
 mn gẖyrk yntẓr ạlsẖryd wʿṭfk hw ạlrjạ ạlwḥyd
 yạ syd ạ̉smʿ lys ly swạk fkẖlṣn fkẖlṣn ftạk
 ḥty̱ mty̱ ạ̉dʿw wlạ tjybny ḥty̱ mty̱ ạ̉bky wlạ trḥmny
 tʿạly̱ yạ ạ̹lhy wạ̉msk bydy tʿạly̱ wạ̉rḥmny sydy</lyrics>
</song>